LNetError: 191018:0:(socklnd_cb.c:1036:ksocknal_send()) LBUG
Pid: 191018, comm: mdt_out00_001 4.18.0-425.10.1.el8_lustre.x86_64 #1 SMP Wed May 3 16:22:26 UTC 2023
